snippet: East Carolina is ranked in The Associated Press college football poll for the first time since 2008 and Mississippi State moved into the Top 25 for the first time in two seasons after breaking a long losing streak against LSU....

headline.print_headline: East Carolina, Mississippi St Move Into AP Top 25
headline.main: East Carolina, Mississippi St Move Into AP Top 25

lead_paragraph: East Carolina is ranked in The Associated Press college football poll for the first time since 2008 and Mississippi State moved into the Top 25 for the first time in two seasons after breaking a long losing streak against LSU.
